The paper deals with secure cloud storage and privacy guarantees against attacks, which are common topics in the computer security (cs.CR) and software engineering (cs.SE) sub-categories. The paper also introduces new data structures and algorithms for achieving these goals, which are relevant to the database (cs.DB) and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS) sub-categories. Finally, the paper discusses the performance of the system, which is related to the computational complexity (cs.CC) sub-category.
